    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、いたいた\n遙子さん、ちょっといいですか？",
      "startTime": 2.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所に遙子さん宛の荷物が届いたんですよ\nただ、送り主の名前に心当たりがなくて……",
      "startTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと見せて……ああ、おばあちゃんからだ\nてことは、中身は多分……",
      "startTime": 18.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！　私がおばあちゃんに頼んでたワイン！\n楽しみにしてたんだ～",
      "startTime": 26.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、ワインの贈り物なんておしゃれですね\n全部で四本……日本産ですか？",
      "startTime": 34.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。おばあちゃんの住んでるとこって\nブドウとかワイン造りが盛んでね",
      "startTime": 40.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "この間、久しぶりに家族と帰省した時にワインの\n話になって、見繕って送るよって約束してくれたの",
      "startTime": 47.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……ん？\n一緒に葉書が入ってるみたいですよ",
      "startTime": 54.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、本当だ……「アイドル復帰、おめでとう\nおいしいお酒で英気を養って、頑張ってね」……",
      "startTime": 63.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "復帰じゃないもん！",
      "startTime": 69.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "い、今までだってギリギリ、アイドルだったもん……\n復帰じゃ意味が違うよ……おばあちゃん……",
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあまあ……名目はいいじゃないですか\n祝ってくれてるんですし",
      "startTime": 83.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうだけど……釈然としないなぁ\n……まあ、いただくものはいただくけど",
      "startTime": 89.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "でもさすがに、一人で飲む量じゃないかなぁ……\n開けたら味も落ちちゃうし……",
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、{user}君も\n一緒に飲まない？",
      "startTime": 101.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "お酒飲めるの私達しかいないし\nせっかくだから一緒に楽しんじゃいましょ",
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……それじゃ仕事も終わった所だし\nいただきます。ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 112.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "……な～のにさ～\n復帰って何よ復帰ってぇ～！",
      "startTime": 120.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "ど～せ遙子はぁ……地味目で、ぷにぷにで\n華もなくて、ぷにぷにしててぇ……ううう",
      "startTime": 131.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "は、遙子さん落ち着いて……そこまで自虐しなくても\nあとぷにぷには二回言ってます",
      "startTime": 143.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（ここまで弱かったなんて……）\n（グラス一杯で、もう一時間はこの状態だ）",
      "startTime": 148.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "らって～！　おばあちゃんにまで\n遙子は目立たない子って思われてたんれしょ～？",
      "startTime": 156.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの……\nそんなの、あんまりだよ～ぉ……ぐびっ",
      "startTime": 163.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう今日はお酒やめときましょう、遙子さん！\nほら、水飲んで水……",
      "startTime": 171.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ん～……んふふ～……\nお水、ひんやり～……気持ちいい～ぃ",
      "startTime": 176.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君はぁ\n優しい人だね～……えへへ～",
      "startTime": 183.0666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～？　なんで離れるのよ～っ\nほぉら～、隣にいなさいってば～",
      "startTime": 192.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あの、遙子さん？\nさすがに近くに寄り過ぎだと思うんですが……",
      "startTime": 200.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの～？　でも{user}君が\n相手なら、遙子は平気らよ～。えへへ～",
      "startTime": 208.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "いつも遙子のために頑張ってくれてるから\nいたわってあげないとね～",
      "startTime": 218.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとして素直に嬉しいです\nでも、頑張っているのは遙子さん自身ですから",
      "startTime": 225.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの～？　頑張ってるの、遙子なのぉ？\nそれなら、もっとも～っと頑張らないとねぇ～",
      "startTime": 234.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "遙子だってぇ、そんなふうに言ってくれる\n{user}君のことぉ……",
      "startTime": 247.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "……すぅ……すぅ……",
      "startTime": 252.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（寝ちゃった……大して飲んでないのに）\n（でも、遙子さんにだって息抜きは必要か……）",
      "startTime": 259.96666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_03-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "……もう、飲めないよぉ……",
      "startTime": 264.1666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
